# Services placeholder

Each subdirectory here will be a backend microservice (one APX project per service).
See `.claude/skills/hc-microservice-scaffold/SKILL.md` for how to add one.

Planned services (from `HEALTHCARE_DATA_MODEL.md`):

- `patient/` — patient demographics + consent
- `provider/` — clinicians + organizations
- `appointment/` — visits + slots
- `lab/` — lab orders + results
- `prescription/` — Rx + refills
- `billing/` — invoices + claims + payments
